---
title: Saucy Beef Meatballs on Handmade Pizza Subs Take your cooking skills to the next level!
description: Time to unleash your inner chef! There’s so many things you can do with pizza dough, why don’t we try it as a sandwich tonight? Form and bake it into golden subs, slice it open, and fill it with juicy beef meatballs smothered in a rich tomato sauce. The crunch of the bread is too hard to resist, let’s dive in!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
